    "section": "A solar generator is a portable power solution that uses solar panels to capture energy from the sun and store it in a battery for later use. It's ideal for camping, emergencies, outdoor events, or as a backup power source at home. Choosing the right one depends on your energy needs, usage scenarios, and preferences. Here’s what to consider:"
}
